result.title: Invitation to Codematics and Algophobic
result.content:
Hello everyone,

Programming & Algorithms Group and SDSLabs invite you to participate in Codematics and Algophobic.

Codematics is 5 hour mathematical fiesta which is going to start at 20:00(IST) on 9th March. Register here for participating.

Algophobic is a 3 hour ACM ICPC style individual coding contest. The contest will start at 21:00(IST) on 10th March. Contest link
